<br>
Here is a brief list of some desireable offhanders in order of ratio:<br>
<br>
.519 -Centi Longsword<br>
.552 -LSoEE with 0 magic damage<br>
.560 -Edge of Nightwalker<br>
.583 -Warrior 1hs Epic<br>
.586 -LSoEE with 1 magic damage<br>
.588 -SoED<br>
.600 -Rogue Epic<br>
.621 -LSoEE with 2 magic damage<br>
.650 -Primal Spear<br>
.655 -LSoEE with 3 magic damage<br>
.690 -LSoEE with 4 magic damage<br>
.706 -Vyem's Fang<br>
.724 -LSoEE with 5 magic damage<br>
.778 -Claws of Lightning<br>
<br>
Disclaimer: I am not saying this weapon is <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>better</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> then the warrior or rogue epic, just that the <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>ratio</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> is better in most circumstance. This is to be used only for comparison purposes. I do not think that warriors will be banking their offhand epics for the LSoEE and I <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  certainly</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> don't think anyone would bag the ragebringer for this. I am just putting the dam/delay ratio in perspective.<br>
<br>
Best bet is to get one of these bad boys and hope that the nerf on it isn't retro active =/ <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udropthe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dropthe</A> at: 12/31/01 11:08:29 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showMessage?topicID=12264.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showMessage?topicID=12292.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12279.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.emailToFriend?topicID=12279.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.threadControl?topicID=12279.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12279.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12279.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b